{"type":"message","id":"c558e8de","parentId":"41171e54","timestamp":"2026-05-08T16:40:21.864Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Compaction not explicitly set. Let me check the session config to understand what compactThreshold is.\n","thinkingSignature":"8561662d54c0d17055b3eca8294c9e1df939a77e6e8d37c6abaa333c7d360f26"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pij80wrwhsfa_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw config get session 2>/dev/null | python3 -c \"import sys,json; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(json.dumps(d, indent=2))\" 2>/dev/null | head -80"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":116,"output":90,"cacheRead":55936,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56142,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778258416939,"responseId":"064d44f2803dc784a6f2c7d3f92e636c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e2cdcf13","parentId":"c558e8de","timestamp":"2026-05-08T16:40:23.204Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_pij80wrwhsfa_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"dmScope\": \"per-channel-peer\",\n  \"identityLinks\": {\n    \"robberzaz\": [\n      \"telegram:1060942816\",\n      \"discord:817750913405157406\"\n    ]\n  },\n  \"maintenance\": {\n    \"mode\": \"warn\",\n    \"pruneAfter\": \"30d\",\n    \"maxEntries\": 1000\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1328,"aggregated":"{\n  \"dmScope\": \"per-channel-peer\",\n  \"identityLinks\": {\n    \"robberzaz\": [\n      \"telegram:1060942816\",\n      \"discord:817750913405157406\"\n    ]\n  },\n  \"maintenance\": {\n    \"mode\": \"warn\",\n    \"pruneAfter\": \"30d\",\n    \"maxEntries\": 1000\n  }\n}","cwd":"/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778258423204}}
{"type":"message","id":"8b1bee25","parentId":"e2cdcf13","timestamp":"2026-05-08T16:40:53.205Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the issue better. Let me explain in Thai what needs to be adjusted.\n\nThe key issue is **token waste** - every message sent includes the full conversation history. The \"compact 5 rounds, cache hit 40%\" means the system is trying to compact, but maybe the settings aren't optimal.\n\nKey settings to reduce token waste:\n\n1. **`agents.defaults.compaction.reserveTokens`** - ตั้งค่า token สำรองไว้สำหรับ reply generation ไม่ต้องส่ง history มากเกินไป\n\n2. **`agents.defaults.compaction.keepRecentTokens`** - กำหนดว่าจะเก็บ recent conversation เท่าไหร่\n   \n3. **`agents.defaults.compaction.maxHistoryShare`** - กำหนด maximum fraction ของ total context budget สำหรับ retained history (0.1-0.9)\n\n4. **`agents.defaults.compaction.recentTurnsPreserve`** - จำนวน recent turns ที่จะเก็บไว้ verbatim\n\n5. **`agents.defaults.compaction.notifyUser`** - ปิด notification เพื่อไม่เสีย token กับ system messages\n\n6. **`agents.defaults.contextPruning`** - ใช้ cache-ttl mode เพื่อ prune ข้อมูลที่หมดอายุ\n\nตอนนี้ยังไม่ได้กำหนดค่า compaction ไว้ แต่ framework มีพร้อมอยู่แล้ว สิ่งที่ควรทำคือตั้งค่า reserveTokens ให้เหมาะสมกับการใช้งาน และกำหนด maxHistoryShare ให้เป็นค่าต่ำเพื่อประหยัด context ไม่ให้มันถูกใช้หมด\n","thinkingSignature":"bd416a3b4f9a385bcca86302df3a1d474ad74160b7e1caebe3dd9da5dfa2e306"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nเข้าใจแล้วครับ ปัญหาคือ **token ส่งไปฟรี** เพราะ history ถูกส่งซ้ำทุกข้อความ\n\n**สิ่งที่ต้องปรับ:**\n\n1. **`agents.defaults.compaction.maxHistoryShare: 0.3`** — ให้ history ใช้ได้แค่ 30% ของ context เท่านั้น เหลือ 70% ให้ reply\n2. **`agents.defaults.compaction.keepRecentTokens: 15000`** — เก็บ recent แค่ ~15K tokens\n3. **`agents.defaults.compaction.reserveTokens: 15000`** — reserve ไว้สำหรับ generation\n\n```bash\nopenclaw config set agents.defaults.compaction.maxHistoryShare 0.3 --json\nopenclaw config set agents.defaults.compaction.keepRecentTokens 15000 --json\nopenclaw config set agents.defaults.compaction.reserveTokens 15000 --json\n```\n\nอยากให้เจ้านายตั้งค่าเหล่านี้เลยไหมครับ? 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":219,"output":813,"cacheRead":56000,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57032,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778258423207,"responseId":"064d44f894a7db8f18f346432351206b"}}
