{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:1060942816\",\n  \"message_id\": \"7788\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1060942816\",\n  \"sender\": \"▫️\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-05-08 23:40 GMT+7\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"▫️ (1060942816)\",\n  \"id\": \"1060942816\",\n  \"name\": \"▫️\",\n  \"username\": \"robberzaz\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"df713c1f","parentId":"644cdeea","timestamp":"2026-05-08T16:41:09.927Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"3ecc04a0","parentId":"df713c1f","timestamp":"2026-05-08T16:41:29.095Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is still confused about the token saving settings. Let me simplify and explain clearly what these settings do, in a way that's easy to understand.\n\nThe key issue is: when you send a message, the ENTIRE conversation history gets sent to the model, and you're paying for all those tokens even though most of the history isn't needed for the current reply.\n\nLet me break it down in simpler terms.\n","thinkingSignature":"ceffc27acc261576ae15ac78b4488154b45a40cf99504e89dd4028138bb0e512"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nเข้าใจครับ ขออธิบายใหม่แบบเข้าใจง่าย:\n\n**ปัญหา:** ทุกครั้งที่ส่งข้อความ → ส่ง history ทั้งหมดไปด้วย = จ่ายฟรีทุกที\n\n**วิธีแก้:** บอกว่า \"อย่าส่ง history เยอะเกิน\"\n\n**ต้องตั้งค่า 2 อย่าง:**\n\n```\nagents.defaults.compaction.keepRecentTokens = 15000\nagents.defaults.compaction.reserveTokens = 15000\n```\n\n**หมายความว่า:**\n- เก็บแค่ 15K recent ตัวอักษร\n- เหลือไว้ให้ฉันตอบ 15K\n- = ประหยัดได้มหาศาล\n\nถ้าต้องการ ผมจะ set ให้เลยครับ? 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":5916,"output":387,"cacheRead":35264,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41567,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778258469927,"responseId":"064d45274189a8b6c2cdbb12838b01a9"}}
