{"type":"message","id":"df751599","parentId":"72703e8f","timestamp":"2026-05-08T17:45:17.573Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"MEMORY.md is 23KB (23388 bytes) - that's quite large. The boss mentioned 91% of 2200 chars which seems odd since the file is much larger than that. This 91% figure might refer to something else in the OpenClaw system context injection - perhaps the startup context chunk, not the raw MEMORY.md file.\n\nLet me think about what to do:\n\n1. **MEMORY.md cleanup** - I can compress/trim it significantly\n2. **Hybrid Pipeline bypass** - I can add a directive for simple tasks to skip the pipeline\n3. **Tool consolidation** - Not much I can do about the 14 tools, but I can note it\n\nLet me do MEMORY.md cleanup first - remove redundant/stale info and compress.\n","thinkingSignature":"3ba1f9945f36e18c3211d8824faa7f23768e62dd1236ba19fd90e8381fd1643e"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nเข้าใจแล้วครับเจ้านาย! มี 3 จุดที่ต้องแก้:\n\n**1. MEMORY.md ใหญ่เกิน (23KB) → ต้อง cleanup**\nผมจะ trim ให้เหลือแค่สาระสำคัญ\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ofcj91tf2enc_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-05-*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -c && ls ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/ 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":836,"output":319,"cacheRead":69120,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70275,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778262302187,"responseId":"064d541f91545df3c32eee28586e91ce"}}
